Alan Marshal (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Alan_Marshal_(actor) 0 Alan Marshal (29 January 1909 – 9 July 1961) was an actor who performed on stage in the United States and in Hollywood films. He was sometimes billed as Alan Marshall or Alan Willey. Alan_Marshal ( 29_January_1909 – 9_July_1961 ) was an_actor who performed on stage in the_United_States and in Hollywood_films .
